---- Changes since 1.130 ----
Added support for the ProxyCommand, CheckHostIP and Protocol SSH client options.
---- Changes since 1.180 ----
Added support for SSH 2 private and public keys.
SSH 2 authorized keys can also be edited.
---- Changes since 1.250 ----
Added checkboxes and a button for deleting multiple known remote hosts at once.
---- Changes since 1.350 ----
Improved support for SSH version 2 keys, thanks to Sean Cox.
---- Changes since 1.360 ----
Added ability to view and delete both Type 2 and Hashed keys, thanks to Sean Cox.
Added ability to manually add Type 2 keys.
